Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At 1015 today, his highness the amir of the country 
received British Secretary of Defense Malcolm Rifkind on the 
occasion of the latter's visit to the country. The meeting was 
attended by Defense Minister Shaykh 'Ali Sabah al-Salim al-Sabah 
and British Ambassador to Kuwait W. Fullerton. 
  At 1045 today at the cabinet Headquarters, His Highness 
Shaykh Sa'd al-'Abdallah al-Salim al-Sabah, the heir apparent 
and prime minister, received the British defense secretary and 
the accompanying delegation who are visiting the country. The 
meeting was attended by Defense Minister Shaykh 'Ali Sabah 
al-Salim al-Sabah and British Ambassador to Kuwait W. Fullerton. 
  At 1130 today Prime Minister Shaykh Sa'd al-'Abdallah 
al-Salim al-Sabah received Commander in Chief of the U.S. 
Central Command General Joseph Hoare, who is visiting the 
country at present. The meeting was attended by Defense Minister 
Shaykh 'Ali Sabah al-Salim al-Sabah, Chief of the Army General 
Staff Major General 'Ali al-Mu'min, and U.S. Ambassador to the 
State of Kuwait Edward Gnehm. 

